Interface IKlighdDebug

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDebugTransformation, ArrayDequeTransformation, ArrayListTransformation, BitSetTransformation, DefaultTransformation, DefaultTransformation2, EnumMapTransformation, EnumSetTransformation, HashSetTransformation, IdentityHashMapTransformation, KeyValueTransformation, LinkedHashMapTransformation, LinkedHashSetTransformation, LinkedListTransformation, ObjectValueTransformation, PriorityQueueTransformation, ReinitializingTransformationProxy, TreeMapTransformation, TreeSetTransformation, VectorTransformation, WeakHashMapTransformation
public interface IKlighdDebug

An interface for a model-to-model transformation between IVariable and KNode. Further informations which are needed by the transformation is stored as an object For implementing custom view synthesis transformation we suggest to take AbstractDebugTransformation as super class.

Author:
hwi
